BugInstance.message: Class org.apache.shardingsphere.infra.spi.ShardingSphereServiceLoader 'overloads' a method with both instance and static versions

Class org.apache.shardingsphere.infra.spi.ShardingSphereServiceLoader defines static field "org.apache.shardingsphere.infra.spi.ShardingSphereServiceLoader.LOADERS" which appears to allow memory bloat
Class org.apache.shardingsphere.infra.spi.exception.ServiceProviderNotFoundException defines a computed serialVersionUID that doesn't equate to the calculated value
Method org.apache.shardingsphere.infra.spi.type.ordered.cache.OrderedServicesCache$Key.hashCode() stores return result in local before immediately returning it
